[
  {
    "text": "♪ Mellow instrumental hip-hop ♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "♪ ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=3"
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to \"Explore immersive sound design.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Danielle Price, and I'm a sound designer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the Design team.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=14"
  },
  {
    "text": "The content in this talk will include spatial audio examples, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=16"
  },
  {
    "text": "so for the best experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "I recommend wearing headphones.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "While not everyone watching this talk is a sound professional, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=23"
  },
  {
    "text": "we all have some expertise in spatial audio ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=26"
  },
  {
    "text": "just from being human.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll illustrate this with an example ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "you might be familiar with.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's say I can't find my iPhone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll ping it from my Apple Watch and track it down.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "I hear it out of my right ear...",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's getting louder; I'm getting closer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "Found it! ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm able to locate the sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "because I'm aware of the direction and the volume.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=50"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you can see, we use spatial audio constantly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=52"
  },
  {
    "text": "to navigate the world.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "And in this case, I used it to locate my iPhone in the room.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=56"
  },
  {
    "text": "Like we saw in the Find My example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the real world, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "sound reverberates through and around our space, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=63"
  },
  {
    "text": "bouncing off walls and furniture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "before arriving at a person's ears.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, the system can mimic this behavior ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "because it understands the spaces around you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=73"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now I'm going explain more about ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=76"
  },
  {
    "text": "how Spatial Audio works on the headset ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the different ways that we can design for it.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, I'll break down ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "how Spatial Audio works within the system.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then I will talk through some examples ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=88"
  },
  {
    "text": "about how to design sounds for the UI and immersive apps.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "So back to this idea of recreating sounds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=94"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the real world.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=96"
  },
  {
    "text": "The device adapts to different spaces ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=98"
  },
  {
    "text": "and adds reverberation from your space ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=100"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make things sound like they're really in the room.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "Spatial audio sources will sound like they are closer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=105"
  },
  {
    "text": "or farther away depending on where they're placed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm going to play the Find My sound a couple different ways ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=112"
  },
  {
    "text": "so you can hear how this works.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=114"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, here's the original sound that I exported.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "Notice how it sounds clean and front and center.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, now here's the same sound but played in a different space, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "like this living room.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "Also notice that the sound is coming from in front of you, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=131"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also that it's directionally ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "coming from the right side of the couch.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=139"
  },
  {
    "text": "The system considers the size and materials in your room ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "to allow accurate playback of audio.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=149"
  },
  {
    "text": "I know this is a simple example but this concept helps define ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "how we hear sound on this platform.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "You may already be familiar ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "with Spatial Audio for music and media, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=159"
  },
  {
    "text": "and now you're able to extend that ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=161"
  },
  {
    "text": "by playing sounds in your apps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=163"
  },
  {
    "text": "as if they are coming from where you place them.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=165"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll be referring to these sounds as spatial audio sources.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=167"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's look at how this applies to interaction sounds.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=172"
  },
  {
    "text": "When we interact with the system using our hands and eyes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=175"
  },
  {
    "text": "we're not touching anything physical.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=178"
  },
  {
    "text": "So by adding subtle sounds to each interaction, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=180"
  },
  {
    "text": "we help give the user a sense of familiarity and confidence.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's an example of the virtual keyboard.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "Listen for the sound of each key press ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how it comes from its location ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=192"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the keyboard in front of you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "Each time you interact with the keys, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "the familiar sound confirms your action.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=204"
  },
  {
    "text": "A quick note on repetition: ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "you may notice each key press sounds a little different.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you know a sound will be played often, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=213"
  },
  {
    "text": "it helps to slightly randomize some elements of the sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=215"
  },
  {
    "text": "like its pitch and amplitude.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=221"
  },
  {
    "text": "It feels more natural and less static ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=224"
  },
  {
    "text": "when keys are pressed in rapid succession.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "Consider this to make your app feel more natural.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, let's look at another example ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=231"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how we designed the UI sounds you hear in the system.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "When we started designing the Photos app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "there were certain interactions we wanted to emphasize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=240"
  },
  {
    "text": "with sound, like selecting a photo from the grid ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "and transitioning from 2D to 3D.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=246"
  },
  {
    "text": "Or when you're browsing through your photo album.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "So, where do we start our sound design exploration? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "Well, we could record the sound of a window opening.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "Or would that be a little too literal? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's have a listen.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "And if we go that route, maybe we can use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "the sounds of moving through projector slides ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=276"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the browsing interaction.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=278"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "While certainly interesting sound design examples, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "they don't really fit the visual aesthetic of the experience.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "We wanted the sounds in Photos ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "to fit in with the rest of the system sounds, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=295"
  },
  {
    "text": "and also highlight a sense of depth.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "We think a good UI sound has to be subtle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=300"
  },
  {
    "text": "and give just enough feedback to be helpful.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=302"
  },
  {
    "text": "That said, for your own app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=304"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can add some character, of course, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "but strive to make it fit with the overall feel of the UI.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "With this in mind, let's have a look again, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=312"
  },
  {
    "text": "this time with the new sounds we designed.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=314"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "Much better.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "The sounds align with the rest of the OS sounds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "and match the timing of the transitions.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "When you begin to add interaction sounds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your own app, keep in mind ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "people may hear them quite often, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "so keeping those sounds subtle is important.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=337"
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, now that we've learned about the role of UI sounds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the device, let's talk about using sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=343"
  },
  {
    "text": "in some more immersive experiences.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=346"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's look at one of our environments, Mount Hood.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=348"
  },
  {
    "text": "These environments are fully immersive experiences ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=352"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the system.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "Each place has a light and dark version.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=356"
  },
  {
    "text": "And both have a realistic spatial soundscape to match.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=359"
  },
  {
    "text": "The overall goal for these soundscapes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=362"
  },
  {
    "text": "is to be peaceful representations of reality.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "They could play underneath the various apps you're using, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=367"
  },
  {
    "text": "and are meant to be subtle, not distracting.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=370"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's talk about some different ways to design, record, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "and mix sounds for these experiences.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "As we began to think about the sound design for each place, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=380"
  },
  {
    "text": "one of the first things we asked ourselves was, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=383"
  },
  {
    "text": "how accurate should they sound? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=385"
  },
  {
    "text": "We went to the various locations to record, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the actual soundscapes often surprised us -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=390"
  },
  {
    "text": "and not always in a good way.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=393"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at some of my personal footage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=395"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the Mount Hood location.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=397"
  },
  {
    "text": "I just love this shot.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=400"
  },
  {
    "text": "When we did preproduction planning, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=402"
  },
  {
    "text": "I would look at the images, close my eyes, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=404"
  },
  {
    "text": "and imagine the peaceful soundscape ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=406"
  },
  {
    "text": "of birdsongs and soft winds in the distance.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "Of course it was beautiful and those things do exist, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=412"
  },
  {
    "text": "but that wasn't all there was.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=415"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at footage from just to the right ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=417"
  },
  {
    "text": "of where I took this photo.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "What you're seeing and hearing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "is actually a large water drainage system.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=430"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the noise is so loud ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=433"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can't really hear any other nature sounds.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=435"
  },
  {
    "text": "That noise reminds me of something else; ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=438"
  },
  {
    "text": "let's listen again.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=440"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=442"
  },
  {
    "text": "Not really what we were looking for.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=446"
  },
  {
    "text": "As designers and developers, we have the freedom ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=449"
  },
  {
    "text": "to curate the best user experience for our app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=451"
  },
  {
    "text": "In this case, we wanted to stay as close to reality as possible.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=454"
  },
  {
    "text": "But if we have the chance to make something more pleasant ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "than what actually exists, we should.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=460"
  },
  {
    "text": "So feel free to recreate and curate the best of reality, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=463"
  },
  {
    "text": "making the sound of your application ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=467"
  },
  {
    "text": "complement its visuals in the best way possible.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's talk more about the audio recording process.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=472"
  },
  {
    "text": "For the ambient background audio, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "we used a series of different microphones ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=478"
  },
  {
    "text": "that record immersive audio, like the one in this photograph.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=480"
  },
  {
    "text": "The goal for these recordings was to capture ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=483"
  },
  {
    "text": "how the air sounds all around you in a place.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=485"
  },
  {
    "text": "We would record all through the day and night ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=489"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make sure we captured the entire range of sound activity.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=491"
  },
  {
    "text": "Generally, we set out in search of places ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=496"
  },
  {
    "text": "with as little noise pollution as possible, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=499"
  },
  {
    "text": "which usually required going off the beaten path.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "These natural recordings would become the base layers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "that play under the spatial audio sources.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=508"
  },
  {
    "text": "We would use high-sensitivity directional microphones ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=511"
  },
  {
    "text": "that could zoom in on that specific sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=514"
  },
  {
    "text": "we were looking for.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=516"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you work with a professional sound designer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=518"
  },
  {
    "text": "they can record sounds for you, but there are also plenty ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=521"
  },
  {
    "text": "of professional high-quality sound libraries ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "that could be a great source of sounds for your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=526"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, once we've recorded our sounds, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=530"
  },
  {
    "text": "how do we create a realistic soundscape? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=532"
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember the Find My sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=535"
  },
  {
    "text": "playing from one point in the room? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=536"
  },
  {
    "text": "We used that same thinking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=538"
  },
  {
    "text": "for placing audio objects in environments.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=540"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once again, we can draw from real-life experiences.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=543"
  },
  {
    "text": "When we go outside, there are many different types of animals ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=546"
  },
  {
    "text": "that make sounds from different locations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=549"
  },
  {
    "text": "and they all layer together to make a soundscape.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "Our job is to recreate that ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the right distance and placement.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=556"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's take everything we've learned ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=558"
  },
  {
    "text": "and create a mix for Mount Hood.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=560"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are two main categories of sounds we use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=563"
  },
  {
    "text": "when putting together a soundscape.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "Spatial audio sources, which are sound elements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=567"
  },
  {
    "text": "that occupy a point in space like birds, crickets, frogs.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "These sounds were generally placed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=575"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the foreground and midground of an environment, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=577"
  },
  {
    "text": "but you can place them anywhere in your app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=580"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the ambient background audio, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=583"
  },
  {
    "text": "this is the overall ambience of a place.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "They are surround audio files anchored to play all around you ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=587"
  },
  {
    "text": "and loop continuously without being noticeable.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=591"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'll use these emojis to represent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=594"
  },
  {
    "text": "where we placed them in environments.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=596"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, let's try placing the sounds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=599"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the crickets and frogs on the left and the right.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=604"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's adjust this.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=608"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's way too loud and feels too close, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=610"
  },
  {
    "text": "so we need to do two things.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, turn down the volume of each a few decibels, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=614"
  },
  {
    "text": "And then push the location of the sound into the distance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=617"
  },
  {
    "text": "so it can sound further away.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=621"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's listen again.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=623"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's starting to feel more natural.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=629"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's add a couple of frogs in the foreground, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=631"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the shore line.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=634"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=635"
  },
  {
    "text": "That sounds really great, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=640"
  },
  {
    "text": "but we don't want to hear the same frog over and over again ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=641"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the same spot.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if we use randomization, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=645"
  },
  {
    "text": "we can create a more natural soundscape.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=647"
  },
  {
    "text": "We could achieve that by alternating between ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=651"
  },
  {
    "text": "a collection of different frog recordings ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=653"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as the location they are playing from.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=655"
  },
  {
    "text": "From there, we can randomize ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=658"
  },
  {
    "text": "the timing of when they are played.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=659"
  },
  {
    "text": "OK, now let's listen to everything together.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=663"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=666"
  },
  {
    "text": "There's still one more thing we need to add.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=672"
  },
  {
    "text": "Remember the ambient backgrounds we mentioned earlier? ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=674"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's listen with the visual.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=678"
  },
  {
    "text": "These sounds are played in surround, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=680"
  },
  {
    "text": "softly adding ambience to the space around you.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=681"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=685"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's listen to all the sounds together ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=690"
  },
  {
    "text": "as it's experienced in the mix.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=692"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=694"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's recap our visit to Mount Hood.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=702"
  },
  {
    "text": "Randomization will be a recurring theme.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=705"
  },
  {
    "text": "Like we mentioned with the virtual keyboard typing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=708"
  },
  {
    "text": "and with the foreground frog sources, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=710"
  },
  {
    "text": "be careful when repeating sounds over long periods of time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=712"
  },
  {
    "text": "Use randomization to affect how things play ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=716"
  },
  {
    "text": "and to mix it up.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=718"
  },
  {
    "text": "Consider placement.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=720"
  },
  {
    "text": "Putting sounds in the distance on the system ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=722"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a tool to move things back in space ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=724"
  },
  {
    "text": "and sound farther away.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=726"
  },
  {
    "text": "And in parallel with distance, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=728"
  },
  {
    "text": "sometimes you need to turn down the volume of an asset ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=730"
  },
  {
    "text": "to achieve the right balance.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=733"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's look at the same concepts ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=736"
  },
  {
    "text": "we used for Environments ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=738"
  },
  {
    "text": "and apply them to an example ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=739"
  },
  {
    "text": "that doesn't use a fully immersive space.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=741"
  },
  {
    "text": "As an opening moment to the onboarding experience, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=744"
  },
  {
    "text": "we wanted to fill the space with sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=746"
  },
  {
    "text": "but also call attention to the animation writing “hello.” ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=749"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here, too, we make use of the foreground and background.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=753"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here's what it sounds like with just the foreground sound.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=756"
  },
  {
    "text": "The animation indicates the source of the sound.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=760"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=764"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's important to note that even if your app takes place ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=776"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your physical room, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=779"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can still use an immersive soundscape ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=781"
  },
  {
    "text": "to fill the space with sound.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=783"
  },
  {
    "text": "Like with the environments, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=785"
  },
  {
    "text": "we used a combination of a spatial audio source ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=786"
  },
  {
    "text": "and an ambient background sound.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=789"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at the video again ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=791"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the ambience added to the mix.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=793"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll hear it echo in the background ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=795"
  },
  {
    "text": "and fill up the space.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=797"
  },
  {
    "text": " ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=799"
  },
  {
    "text": "Whether you're moving on quickly ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=825"
  },
  {
    "text": "or staying in an experience longer, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=827"
  },
  {
    "text": "this layered approach keeps it interesting and interactive.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=829"
  },
  {
    "text": "In your own app, this could work well ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=832"
  },
  {
    "text": "for a menu or title screen.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=834"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's recap.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=836"
  },
  {
    "text": "We looked at how Spatial Audio enables us ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=838"
  },
  {
    "text": "to attach sounds to the UI we see around us in the system, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=840"
  },
  {
    "text": "how sound can play a big role in making the UI feel responsive ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=844"
  },
  {
    "text": "and confirm users' interactions, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=848"
  },
  {
    "text": "and how we can design an immersive spatial experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=851"
  },
  {
    "text": "that's lively and captivating.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=854"
  },
  {
    "text": "I hope this helped inspire you to use sound ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=856"
  },
  {
    "text": "to enrich the experience of your app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=859"
  },
  {
    "text": "making it more engaging and fun to use.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2023-10271/?time=861"
  },
